# OpenIssue: Live AI Processing Platform — Implementation Plan

## Overview

Full codebase assessed. The foundation is solid: FastAPI + FAISS + DBSCAN + SentenceTransformers exist and are properly wired. However, the system still operates on **simulated/manual data**. This plan executes every directive from `plan.md` to transform it into a real-time, SSE-streaming, GitHub-integrated intelligence engine.

